C1 and its transitive Jetty/Servlet dependencies are sufficient for embedded WebAppContext coverage, but tests that implement WebAppClassLoader.Context must be updated for the 9.4.0.RC1 API.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For org.eclipse.jetty:jetty-webapp:9.4.0.RC1, WebAppClassLoader.Context uses isSystemClass(Class<?>), isServerClass(Class<?>), and also requires isServerResource(String, URL) and isSystemResource(String, URL). Avoid carrying forward the 9.3.x String-based Context implementation unchanged. Meaningful coverage can be reached with an in-process Server/WebAppContext using a temporary webapp directory and web.xml; no external service is required.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"JSP, annotation scanning, JNDI/plus, and other optional Jetty integrations may require additional Jetty modules, but they are not required for core jetty-webapp coverage and should be avoided unless deliberately testing those features.\",\n    \"The reported failure is a source compatibility issue in the existing test implementation, not evidence of a missing dependency or runtime service.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_084d6c4a9f48f504016a41f5b20380819780f4a92943e717cd\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2374, "output": 812, "cacheRead": 22016, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 25202, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782707618121, "responseId": "resp_084d6c4a9f48f504016a41f5a2ab8c8197af9dd181594883fb"}}
